{"tid":2446116,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"APRIL玹珠節目上「遭成員當透明人」隔天輕生　網掀霸凌實錄哭了","createTime":"2021-03-14T07:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T09:07:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e22f928c492875750d835406591313e8513da07b","tid":2446116,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"南韓女團APRIL近日爆出隊內霸凌，前成員玹珠親弟弟出面爆料她過往受到的不堪對待，激起各界輿論撻伐，對此，人氣成員李娜恩遭廣告商切割、戲劇中斷，形象全毀。近期又有網友掀出玹珠2016年與成員出席廣播節目時，全程都被當作透明人對待，且錄完節目後，她隔日就爆出輕生送醫的新聞，影片再度被挖出熱議，不少人看了直呼「太可憐了」、「看到哭出來」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5503/d5503346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5503%2Fd5503346.jpg&h=6e00d4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼玹珠被成員當作透明人，過往影片陸陸續續被挖出來。（圖／翻攝自SoSundry Youtube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玹珠2016年5月9日曾與APRIL成員出演廣播節目，不論是在休息時間、聊天時間，她都自己默默地坐在角落，偶爾看看天花板、偶爾摸著耳機，幾乎沒開口過，全程被當作透明人對待，就連主持人與成員進行票選遊戲時，她也是一票都沒得到，當主持人再問到與新歌《Tinker Bell》形象最符合的人是誰？玹珠沒投給任何人，而是把手中的棒子指向天花板，語氣無力地回應：「全部的人。」怎料，此時還有成員虧她「真是天使，妳一票都沒得到，但還是指著（投票）其他人了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5503/d5503342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5503%2Fd5503342.jpg&h=ea4ada38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲玹珠指著天花板回答「全部的人」，還被成員虧「真是天使」。（圖／翻攝自SoSundry Youtube）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玹珠2016年5月9日結束廣播節目行程後，隔日（2016年5月10日）便爆出輕生送醫的新聞，網友比對出當初的時間點，令人心疼不已，現在該影片在韓網瘋傳，留言表示「看了心很痛」、「原來當時承受那麼多辛苦」、「看著看著火氣都上來了」、「希望玹珠以後走花路」，不過，也有人緩頰「當時大家都太年輕不懂事」、「希望成員真心悔改」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dpw94QNAAIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Ddpw94QNAAIg&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfE63eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=9613a0fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dpw94QNAAIg</a>"},{"pid":"a770e3b8b81b24101841f9146c2c8939132136a3","tid":2446116,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac42fef221ed5ea9265c46206f39df87d518eb5","tid":2446116,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"陰公珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc1e38e3dd828dd6cf370dbc0c9fdc41dc99302","tid":2446116,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"無人理就要死？咁連登好多人都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb1d9e45865122f7ac317db6c51b41ae0645bff","tid":2446116,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:03:25.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8bd01a08a8799bd4bda4258711c89e4e4b01cf","tid":2446116,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"又看圖作文"},{"pid":"f0f6e1ecebe2b318813e30817bd16fef7b6f3131","tid":2446116,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"韓團成日都有呢D野?"},{"pid":"ec22fd5246e8f63102a43597249bfeac2615b66d","tid":2446116,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc1e38e3dd828dd6cf370dbc0c9fdc41dc99302","tid":2446116,"uid":260694,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"無人理就要死？咁連登好多人都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />通常愈撚窮 心理質素愈強"},{"pid":"438bc7212cf893bc3125c89d9b4970219458c43